{"tid":1758544,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你咩林鄭，連Peak Design腳架都唔比入口","createTime":"2019-11-27T06:19:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T10:51:22.000Z","uid":45252,"like":86,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"e8dbbddf1a79269bfec2f11bf8a3d69efa0e74d8","tid":1758544,"uid":45252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:19:36.000Z","msg":"之前back左Peak Design Travel Tripod嘅各位<br />\n我哋支腳架比海關扣撚住左<br />\n屌你老母依家係咪黑色會伸縮就唔比入口呀？<br />\n信唔信我買一大批黑色假屌返黎比前線打狗？<br />\n<br />\nActually, they've been-a-shippin' for the last few weeks, from our factory to our fulfillment warehouses. We hoped to write this update 2 weeks ago, but a shipment of nearly 1700 units got mysteriously held up in Hong Kong customs."},{"pid":"dda4155168533058f08d10cad135002a67656151","tid":1758544,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vq2VS6P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVq2VS6P.jpg&h=df2259db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cKP5vTv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcKP5vTv.jpg&h=24d6f0c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n怕香港人善忘嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n想聲援理大手足嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n和理非嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n勇武嘅，推行動 post 啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"73e44c963cbd2fc249e04b51dba78f3a14e5eb19","tid":1758544,"uid":72994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:48:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊度講"},{"pid":"fb76ec4f37753c8f0c2aafb2a55e9c672ccd89fd","tid":1758544,"uid":97321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:32:37.000Z","msg":"我都back 左<img src=\"/asset