994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:48:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊度講"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T10:24:27.000Z","msg":"back左嘅話email有講<br />\n我上面copy左個段出嚟<br />\n扣左千7支腳所以出唔到貨"},{"pid":"7dfc446f510dec12103d1a515a92d8a33b1a8002","tid":1758544,"uid":6848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T10:36:26.000Z","msg":"TRIPODS, THEY ARE-A-SHIPPIN'<br />\n<br />\nActually, they've been-a-shippin' for the last few weeks, from our factory to our fulfillment warehouses. <span style=\"color: red;\">We hoped to write this update 2 weeks ago, but a shipment of nearly 1700 units got mysteriously held up in Hong Kong customs.</span> If you're curious to see the forehead/neck veins pop out on PD Supply Chain Director Peter Lockett, the past 2 weeks have been a good time to do it. Anywho, our Customer Director Jen walked us through some breathing exercises, and we're stoked to say that shipment number 2 has gone off without a hitch.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">We've got several big shipments hitting the Hong Kong and US warehouses over the next week.</span> A big shipment should hit the UK in early Dec. And in mid-to-late Dec, big shipments will hit the Netherlands, Canada, and Australia, <span style=\"color: red;\">as well as additional shipments to the US and Hong Kong.</span>"},{"pid":"9134e50ad7f02bdd4692a258169ce175523bb0ad","tid":1758544,"uid":238013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:28:42.000Z","msg":"等睇人講：<br />\n唔訂咪無事囉"},{"pid":"d427ef4667538bca6a3379bdd97c73ee4f57d01d","tid":1758544,"uid":36053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d75725d5415c4966c130b4094ed843f09d2407c1","tid":1758544,"uid":45252,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"73e44c963cbd2fc249e04b51dba78f3a14e5eb19","tid":1758544,"uid":72994,"